pomProject.name: aircompressor

pomProject.name: Apache Directory LDAP API Utilities
pomProject.description: Utilities shared across this top level project

pomProject.name: Apache Commons CLI
pomProject.description: Apache Commons CLI provides a simple API for presenting, processing and validating a command line interface.

pomProject.name: Commons Codec
pomProject.description: The codec package contains simple encoder and decoders for various formats such as Base64 and Hexadecimal.  In addition to these widely used encoders and decoders, the codec package also maintains a collection of phonetic encoding utilities.

pomProject.name: Apache Commons Collections
pomProject.description: Types that extend and augment the Java Collections Framework.

pomProject.name: Commons Compress
pomProject.description: Apache Commons Compress software defines an API for working with compression and archive formats. These include: bzip2, gzip, pack200, xz and ar, cpio, jar, tar, zip, dump.

pomProject.name: Commons Configuration
pomProject.description: Tools to assist in the reading of configuration/preferences files in various formats

pomProject.name: Commons IO
pomProject.description: The Commons IO library contains utility classes, stream implementations, file filters, file comparators, endian transformation classes, and much more.

pomProject.name: Commons Lang
pomProject.description: Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so standard as to justify existence in java.lang.

pomProject.name: Apache Commons Lang
pomProject.description: Apache Commons Lang, a package of Java utility classes for the classes that are in java.lang's hierarchy, or are considered to be so standard as to justify existence in java.lang.

pomProject.name: Commons Logging
pomProject.description: Commons Logging is a thin adapter allowing configurable bridging to other, well known logging systems.

pomProject.name: Commons Math
pomProject.description: The Math project is a library of lightweight, self-contained mathematics and statistics components addressing the most common practical problems not immediately available in the Java programming language or commons-lang.

pomProject.name: Commons Net
pomProject.description: Apache Commons Net library contains a collection of network utilities and protocol implementations. Supported protocols include: Echo, Finger, FTP, NNTP, NTP, POP3(S), SMTP(S), Telnet, Whois

pomProject.name: Curator Client
pomProject.description: Low-level API

pomProject.name: Curator Framework
pomProject.description: High-level API that greatly simplifies using ZooKeeper.

pomProject.name: Guava: Google Core Libraries for Java
pomProject.description: Guava is a suite of core and expanded libraries that include utility classes, google's collections, io classes, and much much more. This project is a complete packaging of all the Guava libraries into a single jar.  Individual portions of Guava can be used by downloading the appropriate module and its dependencies. Guava (complete) has only one code dependency - javax.annotation, per the JSR-305 spec.

pomProject.description: Apache Hadoop Annotations

pomProject.name: Apache Hadoop Auth
pomProject.description: Apache Hadoop Auth - Java HTTP SPNEGO

pomProject.name: Jackson-annotations

pomProject.name: Jackson-core
pomProject.description: Core Jackson abstractions, basic JSON streaming API implementation

pomProject.name: jackson-databind

pomProject.name: opencsv

pomProject.name: ORC Core
pomProject.description: The core reader and writer for ORC files. Uses the vectorized column batch for the in memory representation.

pomProject.name: ORC Shims
pomProject.description: A shim layer for supporting various versions of Hadoop dynamically. This module uses a higher version of Hadoop so that we can create shims that let us use new features of Hadoop without having a hard dependency on the latest version.
